Package: short
Version: 2018.04.13
Date: 2018-04-13
Title: A collection of shortcuts and time savers
Authors@R: person("Andrew", "Redd", role = c("aut", "cre")
                 , email = "Andrew.Redd@hsc.utah.edu"
                 , comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/000-0002-6149-2438")
                 )
Maintainer: Andrew Redd <amredd@gmail.com>
Description: 
    A collection of shortcuts and time savers.
    An intelligent and extendable 'read' function.
    Formatting classes to help with percents and confidence intervals.
    A two-way descriptive statistics function for the notorious 'table_1', 
    and a selection of other shortcuts to improve workflow.
